    DownloadZIP --> SaveZIP[Save ZIP to local cache]
    SaveZIP --> ExtractNew[Extract CSV from<br/>new ZIP file]

    %% Merge Paths
    ExtractCached --> ProcessCSV[Process CSV data]
    ExtractNew --> ProcessCSV

    ProcessCSV --> Complete([Data ready for use])

